            <description><![CDATA[【我只是头晕，医生却修理了我的菊花<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】最近发现撸铁完铁竟身体越来越虚？而且经常久蹲一起身，就会头晕目眩，眼前发黑，走起路来像是脚踩着棉花一样无力。提心吊胆地去医院一通检查，哦豁！血色素不到110g/L。粗粗一算，身体里大概丢了快1000ml的血！我血丢哪了？直到这时，我忽然想起来，最近每次蹲厕所后，马桶里都血花四溅，宛如命案现场<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FbYFTdFs53yN6oabKCI_Xrw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">我只是头晕，医生却修理了我的菊花？</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hatvs80ddmj20v9afkkjl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hatvs6qbwkj20v96oq1kx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hatvs9ex4uj20v9axvqv5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hatvtf5umhj20hs0ciac1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
